MJ: The index tracks the performance of the exchange-listed common stock of companies across the globe that are Cannabis Companies, Pharmaceutical Companies or trade tobacco, produce tobacco products, produce cigarette and cigar components. The fund will invest at least 80% of its total assets, exclusive of collateral held from securities lending, in the component securities of the index and in ADRs and GDRs based on the component securities in the index. The fund is non-diversified.
